<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <%- include('partials/head.ejs') %>
    <title>About Blogy</title>
</head>
<body class="bg-light">

    <%- include('partials/nav.ejs') %>

    <div class="container py-5">

        <div class="card border-0 shadow-sm rounded-4">

            <div class="card-body p-5">

                <h1 class="display-4 fw-bold mb-4">About Blogy</h1>

                <p class="fs-5">
                    Welcome to Blogy, a platform designed for sharing ideas, knowledge, and stories with the world.
                </p>

                <p>
                    Blogy was created with the vision of providing a simple and user-friendly space where writers, developers, students, and enthusiasts can publish and explore meaningful content. Whether you're sharing personal experiences, technical tutorials, industry insights, or creative thoughts, Blogy offers a platform to express yourself and connect with readers.
                </p>

                <p>
                    Our goal is to make content creation accessible and enjoyable. With an intuitive interface and seamless publishing experience, users can focus on what truly matters — creating valuable content and engaging with the community.
                </p>

                <h2 class="mt-5 mb-3">Our Mission</h2>

                <p>
                    At Blogy, we believe that knowledge grows when it is shared. Our mission is to empower individuals to learn, teach, and inspire others through high-quality written content.
                </p>

                <h2 class="mt-5 mb-3">What You Can Do</h2>

                <ul class="fs-5">
                    <li>Create and publish blogs with cover images.</li>
                    <li>Explore articles from different authors.</li>
                    <li>Share knowledge, experiences, and ideas.</li>
                    <li>Build a personal collection of published content.</li>
                    <li>Discover new perspectives from a growing community of writers.</li>
                </ul>

                <h2 class="mt-5 mb-3">Why Blogy?</h2>

                <p>
                    In a world filled with information, Blogy aims to provide a clean and focused reading experience. We value simplicity, creativity, and meaningful conversations. Whether you're a first-time writer or an experienced blogger, Blogy is built to support your journey.
                </p>

                <h2 class="mt-5 mb-3">Join the Community</h2>

                <p>
                    Every article has the potential to educate, inspire, or spark new ideas. We invite you to become part of the Blogy community by sharing your voice and discovering the stories of others.
                </p>

                <p class="fw-semibold mt-4">
                    Thank you for being a part of Blogy. Happy writing!
                </p>

            </div>

        </div>

    </div>

    <%- include('partials/scripts.ejs') %>

</body>
</html>